OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774642276
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIf the US seized Kharg Island, it
OL,7,Fwould also be harder for the two
OL,8,Fcountries to "find an off ramp" and
OL,9,Fnegotiate an end to the war, Dr
OL,10,FQuilliam said, as handing back
OL,11,Fcritical national infrastructure is
OL,12,F"complex and long-winded".
OL,14,F"All of these impacts point to higher
OL,15,Fprices for longer and that would risk
OL,16,Ftipping the world into a recession,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
