PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774642276
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FIt has raised speculation that the US
OL,7,Fmay try to seize Kharg Island or carry
OL,8,Fout an operation to remove enriched
OL,9,Furanium from inside Iran.
OL,11,FLess than a week ago, Trump declared
OL,12,Fthat the US could "take out" Kharg
OL,13,FIsland "anytime we want", telling
OL,14,Freporters at the White House on Friday
OL,15,Fthe land was "totally unprotected".
OL,17,FWhen asked about a planned invasion or
OL,18,Fblockade of Kharg, the White House's
OL,19,Fpress secretary said the US could
OL,20,Fattack the island "if the president
OL,21,Fgives the order".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774642276
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,F"Thanks to a detailed planning
OL,7,Fprocess, the entire administration is
OL,8,Fand was prepared for any potential
OL,9,Faction taken by the terrorist Iranian
OL,10,Fregime," Anna Kelly said in a
OL,11,Fstatement.
OL,13,F"President Trump knew full well that
OL,14,FIran would try to stop the freedom of
OL,15,Fnavigation and free flow of energy,
OL,16,Fand he has already taken action to
OL,17,Fdestroy over 40 minelaying vessels."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774642276
OL,3,CWhy the US could be setting its sights
OL,4,Con Kharg Island
OL,6,FThe speaker of Iran's parliament has
OL,7,Fdenied direct talks are taking place
OL,8,Fwith the US, while an Iranian military
OL,9,Fspokesman mocked the attempt at a deal
OL,10,Fon Wednesday.
OL,12,F"Have your internal conflicts reached
OL,13,Fthe point where you are negotiating
OL,14,Fwith yourselves?" said Lt. Col.
OL,15,FEbrahim Zolfaghari, a spokesman for
OL,16,Fthe headquarters, said in a
OL,17,Fprerecorded video aired on state
OL,18,Ftelevision on Wednesday.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/18
